## Orchestration notes

- work is planned in Linear
- routed Linear issue authors are treated as trusted operators for Symphony runs
- workers move completed issues to `In Review`
- the orchestrator reviews output before moving issues to `Done`
- if the optional Release Manager lane is enabled, normal workers attach PR URLs and mark issues `release:ready`; only the Release Manager queues, merges, or deploys `main`
- stable learnings from `.orchestration/LEARNINGS.md` should be promoted into `AGENTS.md` when they become repeatable worker guidance
